"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-hollywood-icon-surprising-olympics-diving-career-90s-21318466\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"As the2024 Paris Olympicscontinue, unearthed images from 1990 show a beloved Hollywood actor pursuing a career as aninternational competitive diver.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.547729864611937e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 86, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999968158591, \"rank\": 3.184123367123949e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Years before Fast & Furious and The Transporter, none other thanJason Stathamwas actuallya top level diver.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 182, \"end\": 197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Transporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.557777936994192e-25, \"text\": \"The Transporter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Transporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Transporter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The action movie star, 56, used to lead a very different life, and he even representedEnglandat theCommonwealth Gamesback in 1990.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was 23 at the time, and although he competed in the 1m, 3m and 10m events, he did not take home a medal at the games in Auckland, New Zealand.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"score\": 0.9013000438185039, \"rank\": 0.10773767120093145, \"text\": \"Auckland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7649278876651028, \"rank\": 0.3056551742387697, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jason sadly never made it to the Olympics - no,he wasn't quite Tom Daley- which he's admitted in the past is still 'a bit of a sore point', with both Seoul 1988 and Barcelona 1992 either side of his Commonwealth year.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\", \"score\": 0.9998714876207783, \"rank\": 9.753280627825904e-05, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Voorhees\"}, {\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7797200268334424e-41, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999954377839845, \"rank\": 3.9718803589709955e-06, \"text\": \"Seoul 1988\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999982268206882, \"rank\": 1.7172229338325226e-06, \"text\": \"Barcelona 1992\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999999265583, \"rank\": 7.205652648724436e-10, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He previously said: 'It's a bit of a sore point I never got to theOlympics.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just heard they got seven million or something for the diving per year.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They deserve it.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The divers we have got now are just terrific.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I started too late.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It probably wasn't my thing.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I should have done a different sport.'\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That seems pretty humble for someone who still represented his country at a major games, regardless of anything else.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite him having some level of success - and talking about it before - plenty of people only recently found out about his previous athletic endeavours.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jason Statham at the 1990 commonwealth gamespic.twitter.com/gzqSTjyVtU  @LuxMeaMundiAM commented: 'How did I not know Jason Statham was once a professional diver?!'\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Statham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\"}, {\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jason Statham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Statham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another fan, @blesskatty, commented: damn, that was a long time ago, but he's always been a badass!\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And a different fan, @HYN_SOL, wrote: 'Wow, bro had a full head of hair back then.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looks like a whole different person.'\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's right - he wasn't always bald either.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The more you know!\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the games,the Beekeeper actormoved into modelling and appeared on runways for the likes of Tommy Hilfiger, French Connection and Levi's.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beekeeper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beekeeper\"}, {\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hilfiger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2854275528689675e-29, \"text\": \"Tommy Hilfiger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q3501317\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hilfiger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hilfiger\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, he got his movie break and became a huge star in action blockbusters, as well as Guy Richie classics Snatch and Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guy_Ritchie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guy Richie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guy_Ritchie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guy_Ritchie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So things ended up going pretty well for the former diver!\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with thinning or dull hair?\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the real issue starts at your scalp  Mother's Day gifts for new mums and mums\\u2011to\\u2011be under \\u00a350  The oral\\u2011care gadget making waves thanks to its powerful clean  Dunelm's new outdoor collection will get your garden spring-ready - from just \\u00a33  The exact blush Margot Robbie wore in Wuthering Heights and best budget alternatives  This article was originally published April 27, 2024.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999998617568, \"rank\": 1.3803554362069228e-10, \"text\": \"Dunelm\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\"}, {\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margot Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/